Description: World of Warships graphical resource extractor and model viewer
 Qt6 graphical tool for browsing World of Warships resource packages,
 extracting files, and previewing ship 3D geometry in glTF/GLB format.
 Requires OpenGL 3.3 Core support and a local World of Warships installation.
